{"hash":"28f9978829ae3c45d0093260ea45a5653e263873","data":{"tag":{"title":"es6","belongsTo":{"edges":[{"node":{"title":"노드JS 개발시 CommonJS 방식이 아닌 ES6+ 방식 사용하기","path":"/6/","date":"2020. 09. 26","timeToRead":1,"description":"노드JS 개발시 CommonJS(require) 방식이 아닌 ES6+(import ~ from) 방식으로 코딩하기위한 방법을 기록한 포스트입니다.","content":"<p>모듈을 불러오는 방법은 여러가지가 있는데, 주로 NodeJS에서 <code>require('http')</code>처럼 호출하는 CommonJS 방식. React, Vue와 같이 웹 클라이언트 사이드에서 <code>Import ~ form</code>을 사용되는 ES6+ 방식 두 가지가 있습니다.\n예전에는 NodeJS에서 ES6를 사용하려면 BabelJS과 같은 추가적인 패키지나 라이브러리가 필요했지만, 현재는 <code>package.json</code>에 <code>\"type\": \"module\"</code> 옵션 만으로도 사용이 가능하게 되었습니다.</p>\n<p>package.json</p>\n<pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"name\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"practice-nodejs\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"version\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"1.0.0\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"description\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"main\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"restServer.js\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"type\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"module\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"scripts\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"test\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"echo \\\"Error: no test specified\\\" &amp;&amp; exit 1\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"keywords\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"author\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"license\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"ISC\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"devDependencies\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"@types/node\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"^14.11.2\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\n<p>별거 없는 내용이지만 까먹을때 찾을 겸 작성했습니다. 😅</p>\n"}}]}}},"context":{}}